<title>UK: BA Futures appoints Singapore, London managers.</title>
<headline>BA Futures appoints Singapore, London managers.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>BA Futures Inc, the futures and options brokerage arm of BankAmerica Corp, said on Friday it had appointed Melvin Barden as general manager for Asia and Tracey Bennett as general manager for Europe, Middle East and Africa.</p>
<p>Barden, previously general manager for Europe, Middle East and Africa, will be based in Singapore.</p>
<p>Bennett, previously sales manager in London, will be based in London.</p>
